field.description: Landing/Entrance Page (first 'Page View' event) of a Session.
field.label: Behavior Landing Page
field.name: sessions.landing_page
field.sql:
(select coalesce(regexp_extract((select value.string_value from UNNEST(event_params) where key = "page_location"),r"(?:.*?[\.][^\/]*)([\/][^\?]+)"),'/')
          from UNNEST(sessions.event_data) as event_history
          where event_history.sl_key = (sessions.sl_key) and event_history.page_view_rank = 1 limit 1)

dashboard_elements.body_text:
---

Total Conversions

Total number of hits (Page or Event) that match the goals set in dashboard filters
dashboard_elements.body_text_as_html:
Total Conversions

Total number of hits (Page or Event) that match the goals set in dashboard filters

dashboard_elements.body_text:
---

Reverse Goal Path

Read Data from Right to Left:

  • The column furthest to the right is where the Goal was completed.
  • Every subsequent column to the left is the hit (Page or Event Action) that took place directly before it.
  • Every path that flows into a NULL value is the “Entrance” into the website (i.e. NULL values represent that the user had not entered the website yet)
dashboard_elements.body_text_as_html:
Reverse Goal Path

Read Data from Right to Left:

  • The column furthest to the right is where the Goal was completed.

  • Every path that flows into a NULL value is the “Entrance” into the website (i.e. NULL values represent that the user had not entered the website yet)</ul>
